{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-hide-price-when-sold-out","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1273,"date":"2021-11-21T08:20:37","date_gmt":"2021-11-21T08:20:37","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1273"},"modified":"2022-12-17T21:12:32","modified_gmt":"2022-12-17T21:12:32","slug":"dawn-theme-hide-price-when-sold-out","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-hide-price-when-sold-out/","title":{"rendered":"Hide price when sold out [all free themes]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Your product just went out of stock and you want to hide its price in the meanwhile? Look no further! In this quick tutorial I&#8217;ll be showing you how to hide the price of all of your sold out products in the Dawn theme.<br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo?variant=39850172645476\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview</a> of how the end result will look like. In this example, the option &#8220;Black / XXL&#8221; is sold out.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-current-theme\">Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-your-theme\">Adding the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify Admin go to: <strong>online store &gt; themes &gt; actions &gt; edit code</strong></li><li>Find the file named exactly <strong>&#8220;main-product.liquid&#8221;</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1490\" height=\"676\" class=\"wp-image-1275\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/dawn_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/dawn_1.jpg 1490w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/dawn_1-850x386.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/dawn_1-1200x544.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/dawn_1-768x348.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1490px) 100vw, 1490px\" /></li><li>Paste the following code at the very bottom of the file:<br><br>[gist]e4adadb92e5bdff23a236db2fc0d8b6d[gist]<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>That is it &#8211; now all of the sold out products will automatically have their prices hidden. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in. They work with &#8220;Dawn&#8221; plus all Shopify&#8217;s free themes (Craft, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Publisher &amp; Sense):<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfy